[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Harvest every ready garden plot of the same crop at once, instead of walking to each bed individually.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]One-click area harvest[/b] — interacting with a ready garden bed harvests every neighbouring bed of the same crop that's also ready, in a single action. Still respects the usual "ready" gating — unripe beds are left alone.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Same-crop rule[/b] — only beds with the same crop as the one you clicked are pulled. If you've planted alternating carrot/cabbage rows, you can harvest all the carrots without touching the cabbages.[/size]
[/list]

[size=3][b]How to unlock[/b][/size]
[list]
[*][size=3][b]Requires the [i]Farmer[/i] perk[/b] (the same perk vanilla gates crop-quality at). Unlock it via the usual tech tree. Until then, the mod does nothing — vanilla single-bed harvesting applies.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/58]The Seed Equalizer[/url] — stops seed counts from dwindling over time, plus a rain-grow-speed boost.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/65]FasterCraft Reloaded[/url] — per-type garden speedups (player, refugee, zombie).[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/70]Give Me Moar[/url] — multipliers on crop drops.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/62]Where's Ma' Storage[/url] — shared inventory so harvested crops land in the pool every bench can see.[/size]
[/list]

